name: Signature_Design_by_Ashley_Trudell_Dark_Brown_Table
reviews: Everything I expected and more. Beautiful table and a great value.
description:
This Signature Design by Ashley Trudell dining table features two pieces, a surface and a base. Made of solid Pine woods, then finished in a weathered golden-brown hue with subtle wire brushing and varying natural distressing. The 48-inch round dining table features a pedestal base and an 18-inch leaf. Table only.
